{"tid":1795803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報選出「be water」為年度字詞","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:38:05.000Z","uid":46431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a62873d5ec13c09c9642939af0286afae7662ab","tid":1795803,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》發表評論文章，選出「be water」為其中一個年度字詞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章指，已故武打巨星李小龍這句名言，成為今年香港抗爭者的策略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章指，受到「be water」理念影響，抗爭者「如露」般堵塞主要道路或者包圍重要建築物；而當防暴警察集結驅散時，他們已經「如霧」地四散，「如水」一樣往橫街窄巷逃走；但一旦被捕，抗爭者就「如冰」地頑抗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，這個理念影響到世界各地的抗爭者，由西班牙、智利到黎巴嫩，都借鏡港人的「be water」策略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小龍在1970年代接受訪問時，解釋自己武術哲學，大意清空自己，像水一樣不受型態限制，在不同時候變化，作出流動或者攻擊，像水一樣既柔且剛。"},{"pid":"d9347fa8f59e5e0121acc8dd4de955f720fb511f","tid":1795803,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499368-20191224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499368-20191224.htm&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=d892eb43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499368-20191224.htm&h=4defaf01\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499368-20191224.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4ca8e9620c1ca0bc9678d58c408b7bc36e7c7bd","tid":1795803,"uid":136164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"上善若水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}